{"tid":1374653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］點樣燒哂中共維穩費","createTime":"2019-07-27T22:17:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T10:17:17.000Z","uid":58841,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c4195db5e2eedc1254e6eb30af60a36574255b72","tid":1374653,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T22:17:52.000Z","msg":"事關前幾日睇台灣時事節目（非紅底）<br />\n咁佢就話2019年中國經濟成長率係自1992年改革開放以黎升幅最低<br />\n得6%<br />\n咁我地都知實際上肯定無6%啦 話唔定得4%<br />\n即係證明左中共為左打貿易戰已經無錢<br />\n之前仲撻訂唔買美國d大豆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MEWh5F5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMEWh5F5.png&h=3249b3c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你會見到中共係廣東省身上洗既費用係越黎越多<br />\n仲多過新疆 5年就double上<br />\n所以有咩辦法可以燒到中共無錢正式收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我目前諗到係每個禮拜入紙<br />\n分哂全港十八區一齊入<br />\n反正不反對通知書已經無用<br />\n即係話只要有人既地方分分鐘都係戰場<br />\n一黎可以燒維穩<br />\n二黎班狗防不勝防 無限OT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9448710ceaabe8af58d2cbac25918eccecf51c3a","tid":1374653,"uid":12609,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T22:20:17.000Z","msg":"學葉虎事件<br />\n一有乜黑材料就老屈左支聯辦/支共先<br />\n等佢請成班五毛出黎解話"},{"pid":"bbd937eaa4f5ae4cbc4a0f48b2621483990dcbe9","tid":1374653,"uid":133525,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T22:58:08.000Z","msg":"成幾千億擺落維穩度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"887e1dc89d5f4374c2d6a069051477fe594d86df","tid":1374653,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T23:11:45.000Z","msg":"廣東包埋港澳，所以只會越燒越多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27faa6e98dc19d87d4588a7b747e09884eecdbfd","tid":1374653,"uid":55458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T01:18:54.000Z","msg":"因為有班傻閪係到供樓"},{"pid":"e3d8e4ebe6109f08506faa5616c328807229fa14","tid":1374653,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T01:29:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"232e534a47dbbf62fb86ec1cd27b7ce4fba5bd16","tid":1374653,"uid":215044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T01:31:51.000Z","msg":"應該9成俾人貪左<br />\n淨返一成留返俾3毛分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba33bc3f6671829566aa7f45f3a15cb2d5771b82","tid":1374653,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bbd937eaa4f5ae4cbc4a0f48b2621483990dcbe9","tid":1374653,"uid":133525,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T22:58:08.000Z","msg":"成幾千億擺落維穩度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:17:17.000Z","msg":"呢個係17年數據<br />\n今年應該多到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}